  "title": "Service Staff | Immediate hire | Up to $3000 a month | 5 days work week",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for ensuring set up of the restaurant for service</li>\n  <li>Ensure that guests receive prompt attention and service when they enter the restaurant</li>\n  <li>Responsible for ensuring that customer’s orders are efficiently processed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prior relevant work experience in F&amp;B serving establishment or service industry.</li>\n  <li>Skills can be acquired through on-the-job training</li>\n  <li>Excellent knowledge of food available on the menu</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of food ingredients and cooking methods of food available on the menu</li>\n  <li>Good memory to recall orders</li>\n  <li>Passion for the F&amp;B industry</li>\n  <li>Good service attitude – customer oriented</li>\n  <li>Sociable and people oriented</li>\n  <li>Tactful and courteous</li>\n  <li>Versatile</li>\n  <li>Team player</li>\n  <li>Optimistic</li>\n</ul>",
